    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The current menu implementation is very unfriendly about adding other UI elements to it - which is why I suggested the toolbar.  This is very much a temporary fix as the correct way of handling it is to add Start/Stop buttons to the notebook dashboard.  That will allow users to get a quick view of which notebooks have running kernels.  We could even sort the list according to which notebooks are running.\n"
